  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 394e3525f288a3649be30b055ab1ef28, type: 3}
  m_Name: Hon
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueNode
  npcName: Alty
  _npcRating: 0
  _isFinalNode: 0
  _lines:
  - Thanks, hon.
  - You seem to have some kindness in your heart too.
  - If there was anything you should take away from our talk...
  - It should be to show others that kindness inside you.
  - Let it inspire those around you.
  - So that maybe you too can have an impact.
  - And be remembered just as fondly.
  - '*ahem*'
  - Excuse me, I tend to get quite passionate at these times.
  - Hon, if you may...
  - Get me something with some class, okay?
  _playerReplyOptions: []
